Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 看這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京乃？！
