Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我本打算不去想這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在像這樣感受到小圓的心情之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就無法忽視它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的一己之念可以決定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要愛斯特里亞醬答應就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再一次去拜託她試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到敵歐比特的發射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.64,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(656,660)}ovid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了哦 拉芬蒂 姆奇娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在腦子裏不要去想京乃的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的事情我們會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}即使是我們也十分清楚有沒有京乃在對戰力是有多大的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達預訂海域預計時間還有三十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行歐比特的發射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.56,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(656,660)}ovid
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是遠古之時..的古老故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺綠色的大鬼撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡藍色的大鬼吞噬群星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘紅色的大鬼噴吐黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數之不盡的祭品堆積在大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果為他們獻上內心的汙濁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久後就會覺醒 鬼橫空出世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可將他們釋放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 如果內心不是充滿汙濁的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大鬼就不是鬼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 這世上不存在什麼一塵不染的心嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然間蹦出這些話來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許 這也會成為內心的汙濁..嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵歐比特擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:03.99,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(616,660)}ovid
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用了一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是NOVUMUNDUS的對歐比特用兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:09.05,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(836,660)}ovid
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索儂 嚴重受損
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救..救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯特魯 多部位受損後在與大氣層的摩擦中爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一攻擊部隊 成功突入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分頭行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 敵人的目標是沃克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.49,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(833,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把他們的勢力一分為二呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯·琳梵 沃克斯·伊古尼斯分開行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.37,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(366,660)}vox rympha
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.37,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,660)}vox ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如維拉裘里奧大人所料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 京乃圓進入了法洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正前往格納庫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然無法預測奧拉會作何反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.08,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(656,660)}aura
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就命令各工作人員不要對京乃圓施加壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯 跟會長聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵勢力 並沒有分散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正在集中攻擊琳梵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.81,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(826,660)}rympha
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困住吧 在重力的井底..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把戰火延燒到地表上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉裘里奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？已經不肯叫我哥哥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅決拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊古尼斯 正在和敵人交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.44,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(476,660)}ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵勢四號 維拉裘里奧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是各個擊破麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四號艦來電
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵勢力的一部分 似乎正在朝著法洛斯而來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱法 反應消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對歐比特武器的存在應該在預料之內
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:36.87,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(386,660)}ovid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認亞空力場的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我撐住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}在這麼短的時間內 就把奈·加利特的技術轉化為自己的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 準備一齊射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 法洛斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二區域受到損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞空力場發生器的功率也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換到備用電源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快進行災損控制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復需要五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這期間如果再吃一發的話就完蛋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離一下次全艦齊射還有五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也差不多該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起的時光很快樂呢 姆奇娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就真的..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說再見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很啰嗦哦 田所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法許可京乃圓的出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能反悔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞情況可能是和所有人為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的時候要三個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是晦氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能讓你們死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊古尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.24,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)}ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被維拉裘里奧機給壓制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳梵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:40.58,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,660)}rympha
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正被敵人打得動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦隊有所動作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎正在調整陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把伊古尼斯和琳梵困住..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.91,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,660)}ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.91,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,660)}rympha
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同法洛斯一起..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生器呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速充電中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手無策了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田所君 請再一次聯絡會長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如情況緊急的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已完成出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在接受新型武器的說明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是這件事讓他們知道了 也會被踢下船呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不如乾脆..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然報告晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那之後我又調查留在法洛斯上的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一樣都是顛覆了關於兩萬年前的考古學常識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的助手還不顧避難命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在依然在那裡調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是現在該聊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有趁現在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩萬年前離開地球的人類和留在地球的人類之間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於沃克斯有認知上的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.55,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(522,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開地球的人類僅僅是將其畏稱為大鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}而我們卻找不到在當時的地球上有過任何類似的資料和傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為連傳誦它的人都滅絕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說文明可能真的全沉入了大海深處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻有人留下了石板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定根本就沒有失控這回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的發生過哦 失控
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳能知道小圓也會重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該也親眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧拉打開輪廻的場面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.43,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(482,660)}aura
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下花雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓小圓搭乘上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘沃克斯的不光是小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.68,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(546,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三這個數字出現在世界各地的神話之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分為三柱的神明更是隨處可見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三是第一個穩定的數字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一無法支撐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二將會分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三才首次獲得穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圓不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們運動服部是三個人為一體的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能相信她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各艦準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始倒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離亞空力場展開還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳梵  無法反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.41,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(532,660)}rympha
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊古尼斯 也正受到壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.86,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(492,660)}ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的責任由我來擔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒發揮全力就被擊潰非我本意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把奧拉..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:42.95,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,660)}aura
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我許可了奧拉的出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.36,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}aura
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京乃圓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的出擊得到許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:15:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綠 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到大家身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯·奧拉 AID系統連接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:11.07,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(508,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師心跳數 血壓 呼吸頻率均處於正常值..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AID系統無異常 沒有對系統的干涉..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 姆奇娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人家撇在一邊的是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話等一下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來反擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是沃克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.54,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(710,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著機師的活體感應的上升..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量也一起上升嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是京乃她們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟給運動服部的後輩們去幹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在一邊觀虎鬥麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是坐在山上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們的心能傳達到她們那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊隨時都準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圓 從鴨川那裡..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 運動服部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴨川被..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:18:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我一開始就知道會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要深究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和京乃她們做好配合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活體感應波 遠遠超出了正常等級
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還很穩定！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我壓回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:53.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圓會保護我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 不會有事的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美智？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:19:59.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷 要來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:00.91,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是多謝提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是變得坦率起來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤里嘉諾應該會很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤里嘉諾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 跑到這種地方來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:09.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.84,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛..好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:23.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:28.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真智子老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.13,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子姐她！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子姐她！
