Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
